headline: BTIG Raises PT for Booking Holdings (BKNG), Keeps Buy Rating
summary: Booking Holdings Inc. (NASDAQ:BKNG) is one of the 13 Best Large Cap Stocks to Buy Right Now. On June 10, BTIG analysts raised the price target on Booking Holdings Inc. (NASDAQ:BKNG) from $5,500 to $6,250 and kept a “Buy” rating. This optimistic outlook is based on several factors, including a steady rise in reservation volumes […]
